# GitHub Actions

> CI/CD and automation platform built into GitHub. Automate workflows triggered by repository events, schedules, or manual dispatch.

---

## Overview

GitHub Actions enables automation directly in your repository:
- **CI/CD pipelines** — Build, test, deploy on every push
- **Scheduled tasks** — Cron-based automation
- **Event-driven workflows** — React to issues, PRs, releases
- **Reusable actions** — Marketplace of pre-built automations

### Why GitHub Actions?

| Feature | Benefit |
|---------|---------|
| **Native integration** | No external service needed |
| **Free tier** | 2,000 minutes/month for public repos |
| **Secrets management** | Secure credential storage |
| **Matrix builds** | Test across multiple versions |
| **Self-hosted runners** | Run on your own infrastructure |

