## Usage in Our Stack

### The Dead Robot — Content Automation

Fully automated X (Twitter) posting pipeline:

```yaml
# .github/workflows/post-to-x.yml
name: Post to X
on:
  schedule:
    - cron: '0 8,9,12,14,18 * * 1-5'  # 5x daily, weekdays
  workflow_dispatch:

jobs:
  post:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - uses: actions/setup-python@v5
        with:
          python-version: '3.11'
      - run: pip install -r requirements.txt
      - run: python .github/scripts/generate_post.py
        env:
          GROQ_API_KEY: ${{ secrets.GROQ_API_KEY }}
          TWITTER_API_KEY: ${{ secrets.TWITTER_API_KEY }}
```

### Toker League — Data Sync

Yahoo Fantasy Sports data synchronization:

```yaml
# .github/workflows/yahoo-sync.yml
name: Yahoo Sync
on:
  schedule:
    - cron: '0 */6 * * *'  # Every 6 hours
  workflow_dispatch:

jobs:
  sync:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - uses: actions/setup-node@v4
      - run: npm ci
      - run: npm run yahoo:sync
```

