## Debugging

### Enable Debug Logging

Set repository secret:
- `ACTIONS_RUNNER_DEBUG: true`
- `ACTIONS_STEP_DEBUG: true`

### Local Testing

Use [act](https://github.com/nektos/act) to run workflows locally:

```bash
# Install
brew install act

# Run workflow
act push
act -j build  # Specific job
```

